videos.headline: UConn scores 40-yard TD on 1st play from scrimmage
videos.description: QB Jack Zergiotis goes deep on UConn's first play from scrimmage and connects with Cameron Ross for a 40-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UConn scores 40-yard TD on 1st play from scrimmage) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Pinnix leaps over pile for ECU TD
videos.description: East Carolina RB Darius Pinnix Jr. runs up the gut and goes over the top to reach the end zone on a three-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pinnix leaps over pile for ECU TD) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Byrd left open in end zone for ECU TD
videos.description: Holton Ahlers throws to the end zone to find a wide-open Zech Byrd for a 17-yard score, putting ECU ahead 17-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Byrd left open in end zone for ECU TD) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Zergiotis finds Rose for UConn TD
videos.description: UConn converts in the red zone as QB Jack Zergiotis throws over the middle to connect with Jay Rose for a 20-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Zergiotis finds Rose for UConn TD) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: UConn ties game with 94-yard TD
videos.description: ECU brings a blitz and UConn QB Jack Zergiotis throws a quick pass to Cameron Ross, who outruns the defense for a 94-yard score, tying the game at 24.

videos.headline: Ahlers keeps it himself to give ECU late lead
videos.description: Holton Ahlers uses his legs, scoring from two yards out on the QB scramble to put East Carolina ahead 31-24 late in the fourth quarter.
